  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Design</u><br>Design your spaceship with a variety of modules. Each module has unique properties and functions. You need to design your ship with a clear strategy, balancing maneuverability, durability, firepower, cargo space, power supply, and other aspects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Customize</u><br>You have complete freedom to control the three-dimensional size of the modules and configure custom colors for each module. Note that the size of the module will affect its attribute parameters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Command</u><br>You need to strategically command your ship, set the whole ship’s tactical strategy according to the battlefield situation. For example, set the direction and attitude of navigation, change the turret attack strategy, arrange the priority of energy supply, or even use unique skills to reverse the battlefield situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Physics Simulation</u><br>The game has a highly realistic physics system. If the key module nodes of the ship are destroyed, the structure of the ship will break. The thrust and torque of the thrusters are calculated independently, and the placement position and direction directly determine the acceleration and maneuverability of the ship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Start an Adventure</u><br>Choose an initial battleship, gallop in the vast galaxy, win victory in battles, and continuously upgrade and strengthen your battleship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Play With Friends</u><br>You can invite your friends for a fun LAN battle, you can fight against AI enemies together, or have a fair competition to see whose battleship is the stronger design!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><u>Design</u><br>Design your spaceship with a variety of modules. Each module has unique properties and functions. You need to design your ship with a clear strategy, balancing maneuverability, durability, firepower, cargo space, power supply, and other aspects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Customize</u><br>You have complete freedom to control the three-dimensional size of the modules and configure custom colors for each module. Note that the size of the module will affect its attribute parameters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Command</u><br>You need to strategically command your ship, set the whole ship’s tactical strategy according to the battlefield situation. For example, set the direction and attitude of navigation, change the turret attack strategy, arrange the priority of energy supply, or even use unique skills to reverse the battlefield situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Physics Simulation</u><br>The game has a highly realistic physics system. If the key module nodes of the ship are destroyed, the structure of the ship will break. The thrust and torque of the thrusters are calculated independently, and the placement position and direction directly determine the acceleration and maneuverability of the ship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Start an Adventure</u><br>Choose an initial battleship, gallop in the vast galaxy, win victory in battles, and continuously upgrade and strengthen your battleship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Play With Friends</u><br>You can invite your friends for a fun LAN battle, you can fight against AI enemies together, or have a fair competition to see whose battleship is the stronger design!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
